text: The Karakul crater is in Tajikistan. It left a diameter lake in a big impact crater.Earth Impact database, Karakul. The lake is higher than Lake Titicaca. The impact was about 25 million years ago, leaving a crater with a rim diameter of 45 kilometers (28 miles). == References == Category:Impact craters Category:Lakes of Asia Category:Geography of Tajikistan
title: Karakul (Tajikistan)
